snippet.textDisplay:
Natural aspiration 5.7/350 can go to around 600hp on 93 octane @ 14.7 pounds at sea level.
With 4 psi boost you could get closer to 700hp but thats alot to ask from normal pump gas.
You could stroke it to 7.0/427 and get 700ish hp but you'ed need a good radiator/pump due to
the cylinder wall thickness. The higher your compression the higher your octane.
